{
  "chapter": 88,
  "chapter_summary": "阿飞与孙小红讨论对付上官金虹之策，孙小红以吃核桃为喻，分析上官金虹视杀李寻欢为享受，不会速杀。阿飞携竹剑独闯金钱帮总舵，以独特剑法连杀数名黄衣守卫——其剑只有'刺'一式，却快如闪电、准如毒蛇。孙小红以暗器轻功相助。守卫目睹惨死景象后精神崩溃。阿飞穿过人群抵达上官金虹寝室铁门前，发现铁门厚达一尺且从内闩住，孙小红绝望倒地，阿飞疯狂撞门刺剑，竹剑应声折断。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "无论用什么样的剑也不能对付上官金虹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "那么……要用什么才能对付他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "除了上官金虹外，你也许还要对付很多人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我只问你，上官金虹是不是已回到这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我想绝不会错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "他在这地方无论做什么，都绝不会有人看到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "能杀李寻欢，并不丢人，他为什么不愿被人看到？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "一个人在做他最喜欢做的事时，往往都不愿被人看到。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我不懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你最喜欢吃什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "什么都喜欢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我最喜欢吃核桃，每次吃核桃的时候，我都觉得是种享受，尤其是冬天的晚上，一个人躲在被窝里偷偷地吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "但若有很多人在旁边眼睁睁地瞧着我吃，那就不是享受了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你认为上官金虹将杀他当做种享受？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "所以我才能确定上官金虹绝不会很快地杀了他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "假如我只有一个核桃，我一定会留着慢慢地吃，吃得越慢，我享受的时候越长，吃完的时候，我总会觉得有点难受。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "在上官金虹眼中，这世上惟一的敌人就是李寻欢，杀了李寻欢，他一定也会有我吃完核桃那种感觉，而且一定比我难受得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我杀了他绝不会觉得难受。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽不愿杀人，也不愿有人挡我的路。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_yi_shou_wei",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣守卫",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我认得你，挡了你的路又能怎样？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_huang_yi_shou_wei",
      "text": "就得死！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_yi_shou_wei",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣守卫",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你连条狗都杀不死。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_huang_yi_shou_wei",
      "text": "我不杀狗，你不是狗！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 88,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    }
  ],
